{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Introduction</h2>&quot;Can You Get Off Work on Time?&quot; is a domestic independent role-playing puzzle game developed by a single person.<br>In the game, you will play a worker who is about to get off work at six o'clock, but encounters a series of workplace troubles that prevent you from getting off work on time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2>The game shows some phenomena that workers hate in the real workplace: meetings after get off work, workplace PUA, blessings, empty promises...<br>There are also those warm (unbelievable) remarks that leaders like to say. How should workers deal with these phenomena?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/005.png?t=1727515488\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/006.png?t=1727515488\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/007.png?t=1727515488\" /><br><br>In the game, you need to solve the mechanisms composed of <strong>Chinese characters</strong>, <strong>radicals, splitting, moving, polyphonic characters...</strong><br><br>Experience the unique charm of Chinese culture!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/003.png?t=1727515488\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/004.png?t=1727515488\" /><br><br><strong>Finally, I hope that all the workers in the world can work from 9 to 5, and have a rest! </strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u4e07\u4e8b\u4ff1\u5907","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3213770/39957c019245defadba6db4e22b12d1f2a1a2c28.jpg"},{"name":"\u53c2\u52a0\u4e0b\u73ed\u540e\u5f00\u7684\u4f1a\u8bae","path":"ht